<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_d5824816857c.aspx"><b>株林</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsond5824816857c">
<p>胡为乎株林？从夏南！匪适株林，从夏南！<br />驾我乘马，说于株野。乘我乘驹，朝食于株！</p>
</div>
</div>
